Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:56.82,银日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういや　人間の子供も心拍数速いっていうしな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:53.15,Spoon_Italics,H,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:56.89,Spoon_Italics,H,0,0,0,,I think human kids have \Na fast heart rate, too.
